data.text:
Resources

Dive into our extensive resources on the topic that interests you. It's like a masterclass to be explored at your own pace.

The first issue of Bass Magazine features Colin Greenwood of Radiohead, Tal Wilkenfeld, Victor Wooten, Andrew Gouche remembers Joel Smith, Bob Daisley, Nicole Fiorentino, Pancho Tomaselli, Adeline, Kiyoshi, Larry Grenadier, Dallon Weekes, Kaveh Rastegar, Bubby Lewis, reviews of Aguilar Amplification's Tone Hammer 500 and SL 115, Sadowsky Guitars Ltd's Singlecut, G&L Guitars CLF L-1000, a wrap up of NAMM 2019, plus columns from Jim Roberts, Jonathan Herrera, John Goldsby, Steve Bailey, Karl Coryat, Patrick Pfeiffer, plus reviews, transcriptions, and much more!
